      <body>
         <div type="diary-day" xml:id="entry__1917-12-03">
            <p xml:space="preserve"><date when="1917-12-03">3/12</date> Vm. dictirt <rs type="work" subtype="self" xml:id="bibl_6979">Sohn</rs>. Absagetelegr. an <rs type="person" xml:id="pNt_52006" ref="#person_13428"><surname>Barnowsky</surname></rs> und <rs type="person" xml:id="pNt_52007" ref="#person_15115"><surname>Franckenstein</surname></rs> 
Premieren <rs type="work" subtype="self" xml:id="bibl_6980">Fldb.</rs> betreffend.―</p>
            <p xml:space="preserve" rend="indent">Zu Tisch <rs type="person" xml:id="pNt_52008" ref="#person_15009"><surname>Fischer</surname></rs>, <rs type="person" xml:id="pNt_52009" ref="#person_13551"><forename>Richard</forename></rs> holt ihn weg.―</p>
            <p xml:space="preserve" rend="indent">Am „<rs type="work" subtype="self" xml:id="bibl_6981">Nachklang</rs>“.― Später <rs type="person" xml:id="pNt_52010" ref="#person_21107"><forename>Jacob</forename></rs>.</p>
            <p xml:space="preserve" rend="indent"><rs type="work" xml:id="bibl_6982">Familie Schimek</rs> Volksbühne (mit <rs type="person" xml:id="pNt_52011" ref="#person_18643"><surname>Pallenberg</surname></rs>  ― kostbar) mit O., 
<rs type="person" xml:id="pNt_52012" ref="#person_19822"><forename>Heini</forename></rs>, <rs type="person" xml:id="pNt_52013" ref="#person_13551"><forename>Richard</forename></rs>, <rs type="person" xml:id="pNt_52014" ref="#person_15009"><surname>Fischer</surname></rs>.―</p>
         </div>
      </body>
   
